= 1.3.3
 * Fix breadcrumb under Chrome.

= 1.3.2
 * Fix when used with relative_url_root option.

= 1.3.1
 * Fix error with client_side_validations-simple_form.

= 1.3.0
 * Update `dropdown_menu` helper to be used strictly inside .nav.
 * Add `dropdown_button` helper to be used inside button groups.
 * Add link to 'Droid Sans' font in base layout.

= 1.2.5
 * Fix prepend and append when used on the same input.

= 1.2.4
 * Fix <html> tag being closed prematurely in html_tag helper.

= 1.2.3
 * Fix warning RE :confirm option in scaffold index view when using with Rails 3.2.6.
 
= 1.2.2
 * Fix sidebar overlapping content on narrow displays (iPad).
 * Fix navbar dropdown menu not showing when menu was opened in collapse mode (narrow display).

= 1.2.1
 * Fix width of <hr> in header when navbar is not fixed on top.
 * Remove `:class => 'span5'` on inputs in scaffold forms.
 * Make installer not crash when default files are missing.
   Such as application.js and application_helper.rb

= 1.2.0
 * Make it easier to make the navbar not fixed on top.

= 1.1.0
 * Remove less-rails-bootstrap dep. Only add less-rails in case of customization.
 * Now works under Windows (except customization).
 * `rails generate dresssed:home` and `rails generate dresssed:pricing` now generate the controller too.
 * Fix incompatible use of Array#in? with older ActiveSupport versions.

= 1.0.4
 * Improve doc to customize logo.

= 1.0.3
 * Fix wrong value for .navbar .brand background-image in dresssed.css. Preventing custom logo from displaying.

= 1.0.2
 * Fix `rails generate dresssed:install` crashing when template engine is none of ERB or HAML.
 * Default template engine to ERB in case of unsupported engine in generators.

= 1.0.1
 * Fix loading issue with older Bundler versions.
 * Fix large satellite icon in HAML home page template.

= 1.0.0
 * Initial version